                "type": "Copy",
                "typeProperties": {
                    "dataIntegrationUnits": 32,
                    "sink": {
                        "type": "BlobSink",
                    },
                    "source": {
                        "type": "BlobSource",
                    },
                },
            }],
            "isSequential": True,
            "items": {
                "type": "Expression",
                "value": "@pipeline().parameters.OutputBlobNameList",
            },
        },
    }],
    factory_name="exampleFactoryName",

            "type": "Expression",
